```json
db.movies.createSearchIndex(
  "default",
  {   
    "mappings": {
      "fields": {
        "title": {
          "type": "string",
          "analyzer": "lucene.whitespace",
          "searchAnalyzer": "lucene.whitespace"
        }
      }
    }
  }
)
```

**Input:**

```json
db.movies.aggregate([
  {
    "$search": {
      "text": {
         "query": "Lion's",
         "path": "title"
      }
    }
  },
  {
    "$project": {
      "_id": 0,
      "title": 1
    }
  }
])
```

**Output:**

```json
[ { title: "The Lion's Mouth Opens" } ]
```
